GAME 630: Advanced Game Animation. 3 credits.
Combined Studio and Lecture course in creating advanced animations for interactive games, with an emphasis on realtime characters. Non-bipedal motions, rotoscoping, rigging, and other advanced topics in animation will also be explored.Offered by Computer Game Design. May not be repeated for credit.
