GAME 635: Issues in Interactive Entertainment. 3 credits.
Studio and lecture course in advanced design concepts for interactive game and entertainment platforms and systems. Microsoft's Kinect, Nintendo's Wii U, and Apple's AirPlay Mirroring will be studied.Offered by Computer Game Design. May not be repeated for credit.
